		"description":{
			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>As your blade strikes the enemy, it rings out with a perfect note that echoes.</i></p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Weapon</b><b>:</b> Heavy blade or light blade</p>\n<p class=\"basics\"><b>Enhancement Bonus:</b> Attack Rolls and Damage Rolls</p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Critical:</b> +2d8 thunder critical damage</p>\n<p class=\"basics\"><b>Properties:</b>\n<ul>\n<li>Bards can use this weapon as an implement for bard powers and bard paragon path powers.</li>\n<li>When you hit an enemy with this weapon, that enemy takes a penalty to its next saving throw against ongoing thunder damage. The penalty equals this weapon's enhancement bonus.</li>\n</ul></p>\n<p class=\"subheading\"><b>Power âœ¦ Daily (Free Action)</b></p><p><i>Trigger:</i> You hit an enemy using this weapon.</p><p><i>Effect:</i> The target takes ongoing 5 thunder damage. While the target is taking this thunder damage, you get a +2 item bonus to attack rolls against that target. Level 14 or 19: Ongoing 10 thunder damage. Level 24 or 29: Ongoing 15 thunder damage.</p>",
